Package cp213

Class TreeNode<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

java.lang.Object
cp213.TreeNode<T>
public class TreeNode<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
The individual node of a linked structure that stores T objects and a count. This is a doubly-linked node with left and right pointers to child nodes. The node link can be updated, but not the node data, in order to avoid moving data between nodes. Data structures must be reordered by moving nodes.
Version:
2019-01-26
Author:
David Brown
